Sezgin said that the good Turco-British relationship has created
a positive environment for the two countries' cooperation in the
defense field.
</P>
<P>
"A strong and well-trained army is essential for Turkey
which is located in a region of instabilities," Sezgin said.
</P>
<P>
Robertson, who is on a two-day official visit to Turkey,
said that Britain is ready to further its ties with Turkey,
describing Turkey as one of the most valuable ally of the
North Atlantic Treaty Organization.
</P>
<P>
