Forces in Lebanon (UNIFIL), was wounded when Israeli shells fired
in the direction of a Norwegian patrol near the village of Blat on
the edge of the Israeli occupied south Lebanon. The UNIFIL
protested to the Israeli army and received an apology. The
Israeli army said that they would investigate into the incident.
(Lebanon-UN-Wounded)
