police already detained two persons -- Munawir Anees, a Pakistani
said to be good friend of Anwar, and Mohamad Ahmad, a private
secretary to Anwar at the Finance Ministry.
</P>
<P>
Anwar was sacked as the deputy prime minister and finance
minister on September 2 and expelled from the ruling United Malays
National Organization (UMNO) on September 4. 
