exhibition covers the entire spectrum of computer hardware and
software, mobile computing equipment and office machines.
</P>
<P>
The exhibition, organized by Adsale Exhibition Services
Ltd. and solely sponsored by the Hong Kong Computer Society,
occupies a total floor space of 8,500 square meters at the Hong
Kong Convention and Exhibition Center.
