<HEADLINE> India Allows Duty-Free Import of Components for </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, September 16 (Xinhua) -- Commerce Minister
Ramakrishna Hegde Wednesday announced a special scheme for duty
free imports of inputs for the hardware sector in the country.
</P>
<P>
Addressing the economic editors conference, he said that under
