Andres Pastrana Arango, Foreign Minister Guillermo Fernandez as
well as the speakers of parliament.
</P>
<P>
Colombia is the third leg of Wu's four-nation South America
tour, which already took him to Venezuela, Peru and Argentina.
</P>
<P>
