Yeltsin, Chirac expressed concerns over continued fighting in the
Serbian province of Kosovo. Worried about deteriorating conditions
for people living in Kosovo, he called for the Contact Group, of
Britain, France, Germany, Italy, Russia and the United States, to
meet in New York. (France-Russia-Kosovo)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
WASHINGTON -- The United States admitted on Tuesday that
concerns that the Democratic People's Republic of Korea (DPRK) is
developing a long-range missile capable of reaching the U.S. are
"significantly overstated."
</P>
<P>
