response to media reports that the DPRK may be able to produce
missiles capable of traveling far enough to reach Alaska. He also
noted that U.S. experts have not concluded that Pyongyang has the
ability to threaten any part of the U.S., based on the DPRK's
capabilities demonstrated when it fired a rocket two weeks ago.
(US-DPRK-Missile) 
