Ministry has taken steps to repair 1,002 engines at a cost of 3.2
million U.S. dollars while a further 341 engines were under
repair.
</P>
<P>
At least 1,000 new buses are needed each year by the bus fleet,
but only 200 were available during the first seven months of this
year, the ministry said. 
