<HEADLINE> Italy Backs Malta's Bid for EU Membership </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, September 15 (Xinhua) -- Italy considers closer ties
between Malta and the European Union (EU) important and is
supportive of Malta's bid for EU membership, Italian Foreign
Minister Lamberto Dini said on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Dini and the visiting Maltese Foreign Minister Guido De Marco
discussed Malta's intention of renewing its application to join
the EU, a statement from the Foreign Ministry said.
