was re-appointed to the post after Nationalist Party leader Fenech
Adami won the September 5 election on the Mediterranean island.
</P>
<P>
Malta submitted its original application for EU membership in
1990.
</P>
<P>
Dini assured De Marco that Italy will not only promote closer
ties between Malta and the EU, but also enhance Euro-Mediterranean
cooperation as a means of boosting stability and development in
the area, the statement said. 
