<HEADLINE> Borg Beats McEnroe in Charity Friendly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, September 15 (Xinhua) -- Bjorn Borg beat John
McEnroe 6-4, 4-6, 6-4 on Tuesday in a charity friendly match in
Sweden.
</P>
<P>
The two greats showed flashes of their old form and spirit and
McEnroe also demonstrated his once renowned temper on court by
contesting the umpire's call on several occasions.
</P>
<P>
The two are due to meet again in Australia next month.
</P>
<P>
Proceeds from the match will go towards the Bjorn Borg fund
for promising Swedish sportsmen and women that was set up in
1996. 
</P>
